.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33042,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/02\/abu-hatim-without-vengeance\/","url_meta":{"origin":19455,"position":3},"title":"Abu Hatim on Hilm: Graceful patience to forgive without vengeance","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 2, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Hibban reported: Abu Hatim, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cForbearance is most graceful when it is given despite having the power to take revenge.\u201d Source: Rawd\u0323at al-\u2018Uqala\u0304 99 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0628\u0646 \u062d\u0628\u0627\u0646 \u0642\u0627\u0644 \u0642\u0627\u0644 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u064f\u0648 \u062d\u0627\u062a\u0645 \u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647 \u0639\u0646\u0647 \u0648\u0627\u0644\u062d\u0644\u0645 \u0623\u062c\u0645\u0644 \u0645\u064e\u0627 \u064a\u0643\u0648\u0646 \u0645\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0642\u062a\u062f\u0631 \u0639\u0644\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0627\u0646\u062a\u0642\u0627\u0645 99\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3621,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/07\/12\/good-will-enemies\/","url_meta":{"origin":19455,"position":4},"title":"Hatim on Debate: I have good will towards my opponents","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 12, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Khatib al-Baghdadi reported: Hatim al-Asamm, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cI have three traits that give me an advantage over my adversary. I rejoice when he is correct, I am saddened when he is wrong, and I guard myself from insulting him.\u2